TextEng: Could I ask you some questions?
What do you know about the tower?
How do I get around this place?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> There is no harm in talking, is there?
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그냥 얘기하는 건 문제없잖아, 안 그래?

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> There no harms in just talk.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 그냥 말하는 거 해 안 돼.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> I'm only interested because you're a beautiful woman...
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 네가 아름다운 여자라서 관심 가는 거야...

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Flirt]</Start> Me only talks because you is so beautiful...
Text: <StartCheck>[유혹]</Start> 나 말하는 건 네가 너무 예뻐서...

TextEng: You'll answer my questions or you'll get hurt.
Text: 내 질문에 대답해. 안 그러면 다쳐.

TextEng: You answer questions or me hurt you, got it?
Text: 질문 대답해 안 그러면 때려, 알았어?

TextEng: What did you mean about the wizards?
Don't make me laugh. You smell like a rotting bear carcass.
Text: 웃기지 마. 넌 썩은 곰 시체 냄새가 나.

TextEng: Hah! You smells like bear dung. Looks likes it, too.
Text: 하! 너 곰똥 냄새 나. 보기도 그렇고.

TextEng: Tell me about the Arcane Brotherhood.
What has happened here, as of late?
What happen in tower? What wizards do?
Text: 탑에서 무슨 일 있었어? 마법사들 뭐 해?

TextEng: The new Archmage Arcane? What happened to the old one?
Text: 새 비전 대마법사? 전임은 어떻게 됐어?

TextEng: New wizard leader? What happen to old one?
Text: 새 마법사 우두머리? 옛날 놈 어떻게 됐어?

TextEng: What does he want, do you know?
Let me ask you something else.
You think your people will agree?
You thinks you people say yes?
Have you heard anything of a cult here?
Why you gots big golem here?
Why is there a golem in your room?
Have you heard of one named Maugrim?
You trust traitor woman to leads army?
Text: 배신자 여자가 군대 이끄는 거 믿어?

TextEng: You trust a traitor to lead an army?
How you knows 'bout Aribeth? It true?
How do you know that about Aribeth? Is it true?
What promise has he made you?
I am the ambassador from Mulhorand.
